When youre troubleshooting a possible issue with bad blocks on a disk, which option tofsck will report statistics such as CPU time used on completion of the fsck operation?
A)  - s
B)  - r
C)  - l
D)  - f
B
B. The - r option displays a report that includes CPU time and exit status about the just-completed fsck operation. The - f option forces whatever operation is being requested, - sserializes fsck operations, and - l creates an exclusive flock.232Appendix  Answers to the Review Questions
